      "message": "this is incorrect if len(trs) \u003d\u003d 0\n\noverall, i starred at this formula for 5m and i still don\u0027t see clearly why this is correct. I think it would be safer if we estimated the number of batches, got on extra JIC, but then computed number of batches dynamically. e.g.\n\nfor len(trs) \u003e 0 {\n  // record a batch\n  trs \u003d trs[size:]\n}",
      "range": {
